216
00:11:34,143 --> 00:11:35,843
Peri?

217
00:11:35,843 --> 00:11:39,043
Haibara...

218
00:11:48,352 --> 00:11:49,752
Peri.

219
00:11:49,752 --> 00:11:52,952
